    "en": {
      "title": "Colombo shooter killed in Bemmulla shooting",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "(Thilakaratne Dissanayake and Ananda Jayakodi and Bimal Shyaman Jayasinghe)",
        "Police say that an underworld member who is said to be the shooter in the incident of shooting and killing two people at Bastion Mawatha in Colombo has been shot dead in Gampaha Bemmulla area.",
        "According to the police, a 41-year-old man named Joseph Kumara, a resident of Alpitiya area, has died.",
        "According to the information received by the Colombo Crime Division that the deceased shooter is in the Gampaha area, during the search operation in the area this morning, the police found the suspect while traveling on a motorcycle and at the same time, a police officer said that the T-56 firearm that the suspect was hiding had been shot at the van the police were traveling in.",
        "The police said that the suspect was seriously injured in the attack by the police and died after being admitted to the Gampaha hospital."
      ],
